Section.Name: Detail
Section.OnPrint: ' -- style script start detail.BackColor = iif(_styleCtr mod 2 = 0, rgb(255,255,255),rgb(238,238,238)) _styleCtr = _styleCtr + 1 ' -- style script end

Field.Name: 字段2
Field.Text: This chart is a form of a XY Plot chart. Properties are set as following: ChartType: Step DataSource: ScatterPoints table DataX: "x". Holds the position on the X-axis. DataY: "y". Holds the position on the Y-axis.

Field.Name: 字段2
Field.Text: This chart draws the y value in each data set along a radar line (the x value is ignored except for labels). Properties are set as following: ChartType: Radar DataSource: SystemAdaptability table DataX: "Adaptability". Represents the labels of X-axis. DataY: "[New Transport];OTIS;[Mobile Walk]". Defines three series. Each holds the Y-axis data values.

Field.Name: 字段2
Field.Text: This chart draws the x and y coordinates in each series as (theta,r), where theta is amount of rotation from the origin and r is the distance from the origin. Properties are set as following: ChartType: Polar DataSource: PolarSample table DataX: "Angle". Holds the X-axis position in degrees. DataY: "Value1;Value2". Defines two series. Each holds the position on the Y-axis. Polar.Degrees: true.
